rsucht Nils Dahl, wie der »einsame Tod« in Japan als gesellschaftliches Problem konstruiert wird und welche Folgen dies für den Aufbau eines Wohlfahrtssystems auf der lokalen Ebene haben kann.  aHow is the »lonely death« in Japan constructed as a social problem, and what consequences does this have for the establishment of a welfare system on the local level?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aDeathzJapanxHistory. 0aOlder peoplexServices forzJapanxHistory. 0aOlder peoplezJapanxDeath. 4aAktives Altern. 4aAlter. 4aAsien. 4aEinsamer Tod. 4aGemeinschaft. 4aGouvernementalitätsstudien. 4aJapan. 4aLokale Fürsorge. 4aMedizin. 4aMedizinsoziologie. 4aModerne. 4aSoziale Isolation. 4aSozialpolitik. 4aSoziologie. 4aTradition. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Gerontology.2bisacsh  aActive Ageing.  aAging Studies.  aAsia.  aCommunity.  aGovernementality Studies.  aJapan.  aLocal Welfare.  aLonely Death.  aMedicine.  aModernity.  aSocial Isolation.  aSocial Policy.  aSociology of Medicine.  aSociology.  aTradition.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAsian Studies Contemporary Collection eBook Packagez978311064982608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2016z9783110485332oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070101208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839433072zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839433072423Coveruh